/* Custom Theme Example
   Customize your overlay colors by copying this file to "theme-custom.css"
   
   To use:
   1. Copy this file to "theme-custom.css" (without .example)
   2. Edit the colors to your liking
   3. Refresh your OBS browser source
   
   The theme loads automatically - no HTML changes needed!
   
   Available theme variables:
   --theme-primary: Main accent color (progress bar, status pill)
   --theme-secondary: Secondary accent (progress bar gradient end)
   --theme-progress: Progress bar color (if different from primary)
   --theme-glow: Loading state glow color and opacity
   --theme-thumbnail-glow: Thumbnail outer and inner glow color
   
   Example themes below - uncomment one to use it!
*/

